00:49:57.835 --> 00:49:59.895
Faham, Tuan.

00:49:59.895 --> 00:50:01.899
Tuan Frieza,
Mereka berjaya!

00:50:01.900 --> 00:50:03.834
Kita telah mengumpukan ketujuh Dragon Ball.

00:50:03.835 --> 00:50:06.235
Ohh, masa yang tepat!

00:50:18.235 --> 00:50:20.415
Lihat, disana!
Orang Frieza!

00:50:20.415 --> 00:50:23.795
